How to compile:

1) Install Dependencies:

	You need the following packages and all its dependencies:
	
	apt-get install build-essential libgtk2.0-dev libglib2.0-dev
	
	and for plplot you ned cmake
	
	apt-get install cmake

2) Install PLplot

	Current Stable Version of PLplot is 5.9.9
	Download from sourceforge http://sourceforge.net/projects/plplot/

	unpack
	
	then
	
	cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/ CMakeLists.txt
	make
	make install (you need to be root for this)
	
	or use pre-Built packages

3) Install Traviz

	./configure
	make
	make install

4) Run Traviz
